{"tid":1811004,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"當選者見司長落選者見特首　區議員斥荒謬","createTime":"2020-01-04T10:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T14:45:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe633663c3850537e1b87063285948bdab96d4b","tid":1811004,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T10:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/kXGVxBg6/81886389-989830884730161-4369494431808618496-o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FkXGVxBg6%2F81886389-989830884730161-4369494431808618496-o.jpg&h=17484176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗約見新一屆全體區議員，民主黨北區區議員陳旭明表示，民主黨仍在商討是否出席。<br />\n<br />\n陳旭明個人認為，當選者見張建宗，落選者反而見特首林鄭月娥，是很荒謬的做法。<br />\n<br />\n他又批評，一月六日發出邀請，一月十日就見面，安排比約朋友還要倉卒，要仔細考慮是否出席。"},{"pid":"7059cff3bc9cea58de9b6f958fcb11008af1fcf4","tid":1811004,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"借借位！唔該晒！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">區議員助被停職的教師有更重要野做！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809778\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809778</a>"}]}